```{r}
x <- list(CAOV3= CAOV3, OV90= OV90)
venn <- Venn(x)
d <- process_data(venn)
d2 <- process_data(venn)

```


```{r}
col <- c("CAOV3"= "#482677FF", "OV90"= "#29AF7FFF")

ggplot() +
geom_sf(aes(fill = name), data = venn_region(d2)) +

scale_color_manual(values = alpha(col, .7)) +

theme_void()
```

```{r}
ggsave("~/Desktop/Apoptosis.png", last_plot())
